entries.journal_entry_description: Help the Rebel Alliance to reveal the terrible truth behind the holiday known as Empire Day.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with the Alliance contact in the cantina of Coronet, Corellia.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I need to recover some copies of disks containing the names of individuals targeted for detainment by the Empire. I have two options. I can find these on any Imperial personnel I eliminate or I can get these from my contact in the cantina at Moenia, Naboo.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: I need to recover some copies of disks containing the names of individuals targeted for detainment by the Empire. I have two options. I can find these on any Imperial personnel I eliminate or I can get these from my contact in the cantina at Moenia, Naboo.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I need to return to my Alliance contact in the cantina of Coronet, Corellia.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: There is an Imperial Technician at the Imperial Fortress on Yavin 4. I need to deliver this disk to him.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: I need to visit Colonel Verks and update him on the progress of Tellulon's mission.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Speak with Colonel Verks to see if any other assistance is needed.
